{"tid":1267690,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"好似就嚟堅持唔住，香港人加油","createTime":"2019-06-30T04:17:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-30T15:11:34.000Z","uid":172456,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"61b3115f6d121e5dffed05cb88f36c2973a5b9e8","tid":1267690,"uid":172456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T04:17:22.000Z","msg":"日日望住政府一日一日咁拖，<br />\n香港人一日一日咁遺忘，<br />\n集會人數一次比一次少，<br />\n再咁落去仲做到咩。<br />\n香港就來唔再係香港人熟識嘅地方，<br />\n真係好無力 每晚都訓唔著。<br />\n<br />\n最近掛住發夢職場上比人blacklist左，<br />\n之後都好難再搵到野做，<br />\n要面對嘅野好多好多，<br />\n全部都解決唔到咁。<br />\n<br />\n呢幾日買左幾盒安眠藥，<br />\n香港人，繼續加油。<br />\n共勉之。"},{"pid":"b23be4209651839ddfda90e3a38e1a45df3888b0","tid":1267690,"uid":99024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T04:18:55.000Z","msg":"加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41fecf203b7c89f641cdfe258fe187cf8a010c8a","tid":1267690,"uid":187796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T04:19:43.000Z","msg":"加油<br />\n呢段日子 唔容易"},{"pid":"94f32257c6f97c20079fe89a1218716237a65ff6","tid":1267690,"uid":26176,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T04:21:43.000Z","msg":"英靈殿再聚<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6716dc64868927d1b617e0eebc6556eba653bdf0","tid":1267690,"uid":54228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T05:11:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Yn7ASQz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYn7ASQz.jpg&h=551baa69&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"08cc09e9f23fb0c2ac4ba11ad47b770d9d472e65","tid":1267690,"uid":132208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T15:11:34.000Z","msg":"好撚灰<br />\n飲飲食食去旅行出哂黎<br />\n上個星期做過咩都好似忘記得一乾二淨<br />\n真係冇心情睇人吃吃喝喝<br />\n<br />\n當然 戰鬥得耐都要放鬆下<br />\n但係真係冇心情睇人點鬆一鬆<br />\n越睇自己就拉得越崩緊"}]}